snippet.title: NOBK Overlay Trailer
snippet.description:
Welcome to NOBK Overlay, the ultimate fruit-clicking adventure! Your task is simple: click on delicious, vibrant fruits to generate even more fruits. The more you click, the more your orchard grows, and the juicier your rewards become!

https://store.steampowered.com/app/3172790/NOBK_Overlay/
